This '''list of best-selling films in the United States''' is a list of the best-selling [[home video]] film titles sold in the United States. This list does not include [[Digital distribution|digital purchases]] or [[video rentals]].
==Best-selling films by format== ===All formats=== This is a list of the best-selling film titles sold in the United States across all [[home video]] formats, including [[VHS]], [[DVD]], and [[Blu-ray Disc]] (BD).
