{{italic title}}
'''''Playfair Football Annual''''' is a compact [[Football (soccer)|football]] [[annual publication|annual]]. It is a reference book primarily covering [[Football (soccer)|football]] in [[England]], [[Scotland]] and [[Europe]].
It was first published in 1948.<ref>http://www.sportspages.com/football/football_books/football_annuals_periodicals/?search&sortby=title&p=5&sortby=title (Retrieved 29 September 2014)</ref> It was last published in 2012/13.<ref>https://www.amazon.co.uk/Playfair-Football-Annual-2012-2013-Glenda/dp/0755363582/ref=pd_sim_b_1?ie=UTF8&refRID=1DQ560M3M9XT47D84Q10 (Retrieved 29 September 2014)</ref>

